snippet.title: Melee Fox and Falco in Super Mario 64 [RELEASE TRAILER]
snippet.description:
The Smash Bros. Melee versions of Fox and Falco in Super Mario 64. This is compatible with Everdrive and Android too, I really hope you guys like it. By Pressing L you can perform the shine, giving you invincibility for small amount of time. And by doing the Triple Jump, you can perform the Firefox/Firebird. They both have different physics from each other matching their differences in Melee.

Please consider liking and sharing the video, it really helps my games reach a larger audience.
